data.description: This split entry home located in Lee's Summit features three bedrooms, two and a half baths and two living spaces. Main level, primary suite features private full bathroom and large closet. Basement family room provides the extra living space you have been looking for as well as a convenient half bath. Located on a level lot, you can make this backyard into the oasis of your dreams! New exterior siding in 2021. HVAC new in 2016. Water heater approximately 1 year old (installed 2022). Located approximately two miles from Historic Downtown Lee's Summit and all it has to offer! Great highway access and nearby parks and trails! Come make this house your home!
